LangString MSG_UNINSTALLED ${LANG_ENGLISH}             "$(^Name) has been removed sucessfully."
LangString MSG_REMOVE_PROGRAM ${LANG_TRADCHINESE}      "你確定要完全移除 $(^Name) ，其及所有的元件？"
LangString MSG_REMOVE_PROGRAM ${LANG_ENGLISH}          "Are you sure you want to completely remove $(^Name) and all of its components?"
LangString MSG_REMOVE_CONFIG ${LANG_TRADCHINESE}       "是否連設定檔案一起刪除？"
LangString MSG_REMOVE_CONFIG ${LANG_ENGLISH}           "Do you want to delete config files?"
LangString MSG_KEEP_CONFIG ${LANG_TRADCHINESE}         "保留原設定檔？ (可能不相容)"
LangString MSG_KEEP_CONFIG ${LANG_ENGLISH}             "Do you want to keep old configuration? It may not be compatible with current version."
LangString MSG_OPEN_BACKUP_FILES ${LANG_TRADCHINESE}   "開啟備份的設定？"
LangString MSG_OPEN_BACKUP_FILES ${LANG_ENGLISH}       "Open backup configuration files?"

